PHASE 2: API ROUTES (Backend Agent)
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════

ALL routes:
1. Get user via createServerClient → if no user return 401 { error: 'Unauthorized', data: null }
2. Call service function
3. Return NextResponse.json(result, { status: N })
4. HTTP codes: 200 GET success, 201 POST success, 400 validation, 401 unauth, 404 not found, 500 server error

Create these route files:

app/api/dashboard/stats/route.ts → GET → getDashboardStats(userId)

app/api/posts/route.ts
  GET (query: status?, limit?, offset?) → getPosts(userId, filters)
  POST (body: {content,platforms,hashtags,status,scheduled_at,campaign_id?,ai_generated}) → createPost

app/api/posts/calendar/route.ts
  GET (query: start, end) → getPostsByDateRange(userId, start, end)

app/api/posts/[id]/route.ts
  GET → getPostById
  PATCH (body: Partial<Post>) → updatePost
  DELETE → deletePost

app/api/social-accounts/route.ts
  GET → getSocialAccounts
  POST (body: {platform,account_name,account_handle,followers_count}) → createSocialAccount

app/api/social-accounts/[id]/route.ts
  PATCH → updateSocialAccount
  DELETE → deleteSocialAccount

app/api/analytics/summary/route.ts
  GET (query: days=7|30|90) → getAnalyticsSummary

app/api/inbox/route.ts
  GET (query: type?, platform?, is_read?) → getMessages
  PATCH (body: {markAll: true}) → markAllRead

app/api/inbox/[id]/route.ts
  PATCH → markMessageRead

app/api/campaigns/route.ts
  GET → getCampaigns
  POST → createCampaign

app/api/campaigns/[id]/route.ts
  DELETE → deleteCampaign

app/api/ai/caption/route.ts
  POST (body: {topic: string, platform: Platform, tone: Tone})
  → call Anthropic claude-sonnet-4-20250514
  → system: "You are an expert social media copywriter. Generate 3 distinct engaging captions for {platform} about: {topic}. Tone: {tone}. Max chars: twitter=280, instagram=2200, linkedin=3000, tiktok=2200, facebook=2000, pinterest=500. Start each caption differently. Include relevant emojis. Return ONLY valid JSON with no markdown: {\"captions\":[\"caption1\",\"caption2\",\"caption3\"]}"
  → max_tokens: 600
  → parse response, return { data: {captions: string[]}, error: null }

app/api/ai/hashtags/route.ts
  POST (body: {content: string, platform: Platform})
  → system: "Generate 12 hashtags for {platform}. Post: {content}. Mix: 4 broad, 4 niche, 4 specific. Return ONLY JSON: {\"hashtags\":[\"#tag1\",...]}"
  → max_tokens: 200
  → return { data: {hashtags: string[]}, error: null }

